<div class="description">
    <h3>Description</h3>

    <div class="body">
        <p>There is problem with handling of id's that are created for cache objects to save translate adapter's translations.</p>

<p>The problem is that $data that is used to build holds the full path string for file  with illegal characters that cache adapter doesnt accept.</p>

<p>fix is to remove the illegal characters for tag's used.</p>

<p>file Adapter.php :</p>

<p>the $id crated in line 437 and 461 should look like this:</p>

<p>$id = 'Zend_Translate_' . preg_replace('/[^a-zA-Z0-9_]/','<em>',$data) . '</em>' . $locale . '_' . $this-&gt;toString();</p>

<p>now no exceptions are thrown as the id's are generated "the right way".</p>

